                                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Jangan terlalu sering disiram, pastikan tanah kering sebelum penyiraman berikutnya.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Image positioned at bottom right -->
                        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[100px] md:w-[150px]">
                            <img src="/resources/img/sansi.png" alt="Monstera Plant" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Plant 3 - Sansevieria -->
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-80 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden snap-center">
                        <div class="p-6">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-2">Sansevieria (Lidah Mertua)</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Tanaman tahan banting yang bisa menyerap polusi udara.</p>
                            
                            <div class="space-y-3">
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-600">Kebutuhan Tumbuh:</h4>
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 text-sm">
                                        <li>Cahaya: Rendah hingga terang</li>
                                        <li>Penyiraman: 1-2 kali seminggu</li>
                                        <li>Suhu: 15-32°C</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-600">Tips Perawatan:</h4>
                                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Jangan terlalu sering disiram, pastikan tanah kering sebelum penyiraman berikutnya.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Sayur -->
<section class="p-5 bg-[#C7D9C6]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-green-800 mb-8">Sayur</h2>
        
        <!-- Carousel Container -->
        <div class="relative">
            <!-- Carousel Content -->
            <div class="flex overflow-x-auto pb-6 hide-scrollbar snap-x snap-mandatory">
                <div class="flex space-x-6 px-2">
                    <!-- Plant 1 - Monstera -->
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-80 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden snap-center relative">
                        <div class="p-6 pb-16"> <!-- Added pb-16 to make space for the image -->
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-2">Monstera (Monstera deliciosa)</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Tanaman hias dengan daun besar berlubang khas. Cocok untuk dekorasi rumah atau kantor.</p>
                            
                            <div class="space-y-3">
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-600">Kebutuhan Tumbuh:</h4>
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 text-sm">
                                        <li>Cahaya: Terang tidak langsung</li>
                                        <li>Penyiraman: 2-3 kali seminggu</li>
                                        <li>Suhu: 18-30°C</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-600">Tips Perawatan:</h4>
                                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Potong daun tua yang <br>
                                        menguning, gunakan pupuk<br>
                                        cair sebulan sekali, dan <br>
                                        bersihkan daun dari debu.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Image positioned at bottom right -->
                        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[100px] md:w-[150px]">
                            <img src="/resources/img/mons.png" alt="Monstera Plant" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Plant 2 - Aglaonema -->
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-80 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden snap-center relative">
                        <div class="p-6 pb-16"> <!-- Added pb-16 to make space for the image -->
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-2">Aglaonema</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Tanaman dengan daun berwarna-warni, sering disebut "Sri Rejeki".</p>
                            
                            <div class="space-y-3">
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-600">Kebutuhan Tumbuh:</h4>
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 text-sm">
                                        <li>Cahaya: Redup hingga sedang</li>
                                        <li>Penyiraman: 2-3 kali seminggu</li>
                                        <li>Suhu: 20-30°C</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-600">Tips Perawatan:</h4>
                                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Hindari sinar matahari langsung,<br> bersihkan daun agar tetap segar.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Image positioned at bottom right -->
                        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[100px] md:w-[150px]">
                            <img src="/resources/img/aglo.png" alt="Monstera Plant" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Plant 3 - Sansevieria -->
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-80 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden snap-center relative">
                        <div class="p-6 pb-16"> <!-- Added pb-16 to make space for the image -->
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-2">Sansevieria (Lidah Mertua)</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Tanaman tahan banting yang bisa menyerap polusi udara.</p>
                            
                            <div class="space-y-3">
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-600">Kebutuhan Tumbuh:</h4>
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 text-sm">
                                        <li>Cahaya: Redup hingga terang</li>
                                        <li>Penyiraman: 1-2 kali seminggu</li>
                                        <li>Suhu: 15-32°C</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-600">Tips Perawatan:</h4>
                                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Jangan terlalu sering disiram, pastikan tanah kering sebelum penyiraman berikutnya.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Image positioned at bottom right -->
                        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[100px] md:w-[150px]">
                            <img src="/resources/img/sansi.png" alt="Monstera Plant" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Plant 3 - Sansevieria -->
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-80 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden snap-center">
                        <div class="p-6">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-2">Sansevieria (Lidah Mertua)</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Tanaman tahan banting yang bisa menyerap polusi udara.</p>
                            
                            <div class="space-y-3">
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-600">Kebutuhan Tumbuh:</h4>
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 text-sm">
                                        <li>Cahaya: Rendah hingga terang</li>
                                        <li>Penyiraman: 1-2 kali seminggu</li>
                                        <li>Suhu: 15-32°C</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-600">Tips Perawatan:</h4>
                                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Jangan terlalu sering disiram, pastikan tanah kering sebelum penyiraman berikutnya.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .hide-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {
        display: none;
    }
    .hide-scrollbar {
        -ms-overflow-style: none;
        scrollbar-width: none;
    }
    .snap-x {
        scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    }
    .snap-center {
        scroll-snap-align: center;
    }
</style>

<script>
    // Optional JavaScript for arrow navigation
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
        const carousel = document.querySelector('.hide-scrollbar');
        const prevBtn = document.querySelector('button[class*="left-2"]');
        const nextBtn = document.querySelector('button[class*="right-2"]');
        
        if (prevBtn && nextBtn) {
            prevBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                carousel.scrollBy({ left: -300, behavior: 'smooth' });
            });
            
            nextBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                carousel.scrollBy({ left: 300, behavior: 'smooth' });
            });
        }
    });
</script>

